Revision history for Perl-Critic-Bangs

NEXT
        [FIXES]
        fixed bug in ProhibitCommentedOutCode which prevented custom configuration from working

        [ENHANCEMENTS]
        Added utf8 to the list of exceptions in ProhibitNumberedNames.
        The exceptions are also now case-insensitive.
        Added ProhibitUselessRegexModifiers.pm policy
        switched to testing method that Perl::Critic uses


